\title{tidybrreg: Tidy Interface to Norway's Central Business Registry ('Enhetsregisteret')}
\description{
A tidy interface to download, search, and analyze data from the Norwegian Central Coordinating Register for Legal Entities (Enhetsregisteret), maintained by the Brønnøysund Register Centre. Provides access to registration data for approximately 1 million legal entities including companies, partnerships, sole proprietorships, associations, and government bodies. Returns tibbles with English column names translated to English via a data-driven dictionary; unknown API fields pass through with auto-generated names. Coded values (legal forms, industry codes, roles) can be translated to English on demand using bundled reference data or live lookups from the SSB Klass API. Data is freely available under the Norwegian Licence for Open Government Data (NLOD 2.0).
